<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Edict" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Édict</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Edíct,</orth> decree, law: <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 11</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.151" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 151</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.3.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 3, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.258" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 258</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.203" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 203</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 111</bibl>. <cit><quote>make thine own e. for thy pains, which we will answer as a law,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.12.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 12, 32</bibl></cit> (i. e. decree the reward for thy pains).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>